# From https://www.reddit.com/r/linux/comments/3ly2zl/lpt_use_python_interpreter_as_an_advanced/

cat <<EOM
Python load with mathematic functions.

Functions:

  **   (power)
  sqrt

  log
  sin (in radians)
  cos (in radians)
  tan (in radians)

Constants:

  e
  pi


x = ( sin(pi/6)*cos(pi/6) )**2 + sqrt(2/3)
x

From https://www.reddit.com/r/linux/comments/3ly2zl/lpt_use_python_interpreter_as_an_advanced/
EOM
python -ic "from math import *; import cmath"
